# TikTok Live Stream Plugin

The TikTok Live Stream Plugin allows you to embed TikTok live streams on your WordPress website and collect feedback from your audience.

## Features

- Display TikTok live streams on your website.
- Collect feedback from viewers with a customizable feedback form.
- Display the live stream and feedback form together on any post, page, or widgetized area.

## Installation

1. Download the plugin zip file from the GitHub repository.
2. In your WordPress admin panel, navigate to Plugins > Add New.
3. Click on the "Upload Plugin" button, select the plugin zip file, and click "Install Now."
4. Activate the plugin.

## Usage

### Shortcode

Use the following shortcode to display the TikTok live stream and feedback form together on any post or page:

```
[tiktok_live_stream_with_feedback]
```

Use the following shortcode to embed a TikTok live stream on any page or post:

```
[tiktok_live_stream username="example_username"]
Replace USERNAME with your TikTok username.

```

### Widget

You can also use the TikTok Live Stream Widget to display the live stream and feedback form together in a widgetized area of your theme.

1. Go to Appearance > Widgets in your WordPress admin panel.
2. Drag the "TikTok Live Stream Widget" to the desired widget area.
3. Enter your TikTok Username and URL or TikTok Profile ID in the widget settings.

### Feedback Form and Live Stream Together

You can display the live stream and feedback form together by using the shortcode or widget in your posts, pages, or widgetized areas. This allows your audience to watch the live stream and submit feedback simultaneously, enhancing user engagement and interaction.

## Configuration

Before using the plugin, you'll need to obtain your TikTok Username and URL or TikTok Profile ID:

1. **TikTok Username**: Enter your TikTok Username.
2. **TikTok URL or Profile ID**: Provide the URL of your TikTok profile or the Profile ID.

Once you have obtained this information, you can configure the plugin settings in the WordPress admin panel.

## Compatibility

This plugin is compatible with all modern WordPress themes. However, some themes or plugins may require additional styling adjustments for optimal display.

